>\n9月9日美國國會加速香港人權法案既大日子<br />\n10月1日制裁支那<br />\n<br />\n無論係支那定美國，都想係101之前做個了結<br />\n所以無論如何一定要撐到101"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:17:05.000Z","msg":"關於文宣攻勢 其實我已經寫左個大概<br />\n而家要同港共鬥拉中間派<br />\n［藍絲文宣方向第一波攻勢］打破舊有思想：共產黨好撚強大<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434563/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434563/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n集會我目前諗到既係 西環同尖沙咀一定要有"},{"pid":"d107eea3328e629f6817face4e8799f166376d27","tid":1438594,"uid":109320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:17:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe6375842ac84736a991efecdb0a52d90b263a23","tid":1438594,"uid":169646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:18:18.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n第三點, 罷買應該會容易D<br />\n例如罷去商務, 去大眾買書<br />\n唔去M記/吉野家, 去非藍屍小店等等"},{"pid":"111090671819722308bcfb8a5e53ea2319bad41f","tid":1438594,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:22:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9d3b7a6ba0585b59bced44d523a29c2a1d3ec3","tid":1438594,"uid":31501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:26:44.000Z","msg":"當年雨革死左分化<br />\n只要團結不分化就冇問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854e078e68e1b13b771a03a92d49b56c6c522cc2","tid":1438594,"uid":31501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年雨革死在分化<br />\n只要團結不分化就冇問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"12ef8ae8cca21e8150704dc650e9cd5282e07eb6","tid":1438594,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"854e078e68e1b13b771a03a92d49b56c6c522cc2","tid":1438594,"uid":31501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年雨革死在分化<br />\n只要團結不分化就冇問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq